snippet.title: Christmas For #GOSH - Johnny Depp CHARITY Stream🎄🎅
snippet.description:
The goal of this event, Christmas For #GOSH - Johnny Depp CHARITY Stream, is to raise money in support of children and families who need the use of life-saving medical equipment. There are so many generous people in the world who can and DO help. 

One of those people is JOHNNY DEPP, a man whose own daughter was treated at GOSH.

 Therefore all money raised will go to Great Ormond Street Hospital where Johnny Depp himself donates millions every year.

In recent years Johnny Depp has faced numerous challenges while displaying the upmost humility, honesty, strength and perseverance.

As supporters of Johnny Depp this is a great opportunity to follow his lead by putting a smile on the face children, especially at Christmas time.

Contact me - https://linktr.ee/steviejraw

Help me open a Domestic Violence Shelter For Men -
https://igg.me/at/steviejsrefugeformen/x/26939005#/

Art Of Elysium Donation Page - https://www.pledge.to/the-art-of-elysium

Have an awesome day!

THANKS FOR WATCHING!!
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #TeamGOSH #Charity
